    Format

    spain_provinces

    A sf object with 60 rows and 4 columns:

    OBJECTID
    codigo
    nombre
    geometry

    Source

    https://github.com/koldLight/curso-r-dataviz/blob/master/dat/spain_provinces.geojson

    See also

    https://github.com/jrosell/jrrosell/blob/main/data/spain_provinces.rda
